    About this item

    • Thicker Metal, More Sturdy: Made of premium aluminum alloy, UGREEN phone stand is solid and steady. It allows you to adjust different angles with no worry about tipping over. The heavy base stands your iPhone just perfectly as you want. The elegant design with smooth metal makes this phone holder a very nice finish, a worthy choice for those people pursuing product quality.
    • Choose Preferred Viewing Angle: With multi-angle adjustable, this desk cell phone holder allows you to simply adjust and choose comfortable angles. Two rotation axes of this aluminum stand achieve the height fine-adjustment to some extent, thus keeping an excellent sight view and relieving your neck pain.
    • Compatible for 4.7-7.9 Inch Phone: This handphone stand fits for 4.7" to Max 7.9" mobile phones and supports Max 0.47 inches thickness for the phone with a case. It's compatible with Apple iPhone 12 11 Pro Max, iPhone 12 mini, new iPhone SE, iPhone XS XR X 8plus 7 6S 6 Plus, iPad mini, Samsung Galaxy Note 20 S20 Ultra S10 S10e S10+ Note 9 8 S9 S8 Plus S7 Edge S6, LG G7 G8 V40 ThinQ V20 V30, Google Pixel 4 3a 3 2 XL, Motorola Moto G7 G6, OnePlus 7 6T 6 5T 5 and more.
    • Easy to Carry On-The-Go: With a compact folded size of 4.72"x 3.94"x 3", UGREEN cellphone stand is portable for travel, home and office.
    • Easy to Connect a Charger: With a charging port design, this phone dock can stand your phone easily while charging and you can charge your iphone vertically.

    Product Description

    Sturdy, Adjustable& Foldable

    Made of premium aluminum alloy, UGREEN cell phone stand has a sturdy and metal base, holding your smartphone steady without tipping over. With an elegant design and nice finish, this metal phone dock is a perfect companion when you're watching video, reading, video recording, browsing the web, playing games or facetime call. It also allows you stand your phone vertically with the charging port reserved, no blocking to a charger.

    Broad Compatibility

    This universal phone cradle stand fits for 4.7 to Max 7.9 Inch mobile phones. Max thickness allowed for the phone with a case is 0.47 inches.

    Compatible with Apple iPhone 12 11 Pro Max, iPhone 12 mini, iPhone 11 promax, iPhone 12 promax, iPhone XS Max XR X 8 Plus 7 Plus 6S, iPad mini, Samsung Note 10 Note 10+, Note9 S9 Plus Note 8 S8 S8+, Galaxy A80 A70 A60 A40s A20 A10, etc.

    Protect Your Phone with Anti-scratches

    Anti-slip on the Bottom, Steady and Firm

    Multi-angle Adjustable, Comfortable Sight View

        5.0 out of 5 stars built like a tank
        Reviewed in the United States on September 1, 2020
        Verified Purchase
        i have lost count of how many compact folding stands i have purchased for my kindle or phone. more than a dozen, easily... and at last, i have found 'the one'... with other stands, they either dont have the adjustability i need, OR theyre cheaply manufactured and wind up cracked or broken after being tossed around in my bag or luggage. i am 100% positive that will never happen with this stand, as it is built like a tank... every part of it is metal, THICK metal at that... its a bit heavy, and a bit bulkier than some other stands ive used, but i can tell you one thing for sure, its not going to break on you. it is easily adjustable to pretty much any angle you could want, and the 'hooks' that hold whatever it is youre putting on it are large enough for just about any device you might want to use it with, including my phone with a fairly thick case, and my kindle with a folding cover. the rubber pads on the hooks cover the entire surface, they arent dinky little stick-ons that dont have enough coverage, or will come off after light usage... and the non-slip pad on the bottom covers the entire base. it is super grippy, wont slide, and wont scratch whatever surface youre using it on.

        the only way this could be any better is if it were made of titanium, to make it lighter and thinner with the same durability... UGREEN, take note, i would cheerfully pay you 5x the price for this stand in titanium. seriously. like right this instant.

        Dr. Danger Mousette
        5.0 out of 5 stars Beautifully engineered and useful phone stand
        Reviewed in the United Kingdom on July 10, 2021
        Verified Purchase
         I bought this because I do quite a lot of Zoom and Facetime calls, and I have to say, it fits the bill perfectly.

        Pros:
        - No more propping up your phone on the side of a coffee cup ever again.
        - Really nicely engineered. It has a good weight to it, a lovely finish, and beautifully calculated resistance joints. Whoever designed it has real attention to detail.
        - Can easily hold not just a phone, but a tablet as well (a tablet with a case on it actually).
        - There is a 'cut-out' in the stand so that you simultaneously talk whilst the phone is charging.
        - There are soft rubber pads on the stand in strategic places to make sure your phone / tablet casing doesn't get scratched.
        - It comes with a 2 year warranty which is hidden in the bottom of the box.

        Cons:
        - No idea why it's called a Phone Holder with Roller. What is the roller? and what is it for?
        - No instructions, but it is fairly easy to figure out.
        - No height adjustability. Maybe one day they could design a tripod that fits in the bottom. That would make it the complete package and enable it to be used for things like vlogging.
        - The charging cable can be difficult to fit once the phone is on the stand. Ideally you need one with a 90 degree connection.

        All in all, a great product that I use daily.
